The evidence with the title 'Parents charged with 'neglect' after 11-year-old plays in yard for ... ' says Jun 14, 2015  ... Two Florida parents were hit with felony neglect charges after their 11 - year - old son was reportedly playing alone in the backyard for an hour andahalf.According to his mother, the boy arrived home before his parents and was locked out of the house, so he shot some hoops in the yard until they arrived. 
